{"parse":{"title":"grape","pageid":4847,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"==English==\n{{wp}}\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{enPR|grāp}}\n* {{IPA|en|/ɡɹeɪp/|a=RP,GenAm,CanE}}\n** {{audio|en|en-uk-grape.ogg|a=UK}}\n** {{audio|en|en-us-grape.ogg|a=US}}\n* {{IPA|en|/ɡɹæɪp/|a=AuE,NZE}}\n* {{IPA|en|/ɡɹep/|a=ScE}}\n{{rfap|en|{{w|Canadian English|Canada}}}}\n* {{rhymes|en|eɪp|s=1}}\n* {{hyph|en|grape}}\n\n===Etymology 1===\n[[File:Grapes05.jpg|thumb|upright|A bunch of '''grapes''' ({{senseno|en|Q10978}})]]\n{{ety|en|id=wine-berry|nodot=1|text=*|:inh|enm:grape<ety:bor<fro:grappe<t:cluster of fruit or flowers, bunch of grapes><ety:deverbal<graper<t:to pick grapes><lit:to hook><ety:bor<frk:*krappō<t:to hook><ety:der<ine-pro:*greb-<t:hook><ety:from<*ger-<t:to turn, bend, twist>>>><ine-pro:*gremb-<t:crooked, uneven><ety:from<*ger-<t:to turn, bend, twist>>>>>>>>>>>}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*ger-|t=to turn, bend, twist}} {{displaced|ang|wīnberġe|t=grape|lit=wine-berry}}. Cognate with {{cog|dum|krappe|t=hook}}, {{cog|goh|krapfo|t=hook}} (whence {{cog|de|Krapfen|t=Berliner doughnut}}. {{doublet|en|grappa}}. More at {{m|en|cramp}}.\n\n====Noun====\n{{en-noun|~}}\n\n# {{senseid|en|Q10978}} {{lb|en|countable}} A small, round, smooth-skinned edible [[fruit]], usually purple, red, or green, that grows in [[bunch]]es on female vines of most species of genus {{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}} and the self-fertile plants of species {{taxfmt|Vitis vinifera|species}}.\n#: {{ux|en|'''Grapes''' give us whole-fruit snacks, grape juice, raisins, wine, and more.}}\n# {{lb|en|countable|uncountable}} Any woody [[vine]] of genus {{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}} that bears clusters of grapes; a [[grapevine]].\n#: {{ux|en|wild '''grape''' covering the back slope}}\n# {{lb|en|countable}} Any of various [[fruit]]s or [[plant]]s with varying resemblances to those of genus ''Vitis'' but belonging to other genera, not necessarily edible.\n#: {{ux|en|sea '''grape'''; tail '''grape'''}}\n# {{lb|en|countable|uncountable}} A dark [[purple|purplish]]-[[red]] [[colour]], the colour of many grapes.\n#: {{ux|en|For those seeking purply tones, the paint colors available include mauve, magenta, and '''grape'''.}}\n#: {{color panel|6f2da8}}\n# {{lb|en|uncountable}} {{clipping of|en|grapeshot}}.\n#: {{ux|en|men mowed down by '''grape'''}}\n#* {{RQ:Poe Pym|XX||pages=165{{ndash}}166|pageref=166|The boarding-nettings were up, the guns double-shotted with '''grape''' and canister, and the swivels loaded with canisters of musket-balls.}}\n# {{lb|en|pathology}} A [[mangy]] [[tumour]] on a [[horse]]'s [[leg]].\n# {{lb|en|US|naval|_|slang}} A purple-shirted [[technician]] responsible for [[refuel]]ing [[aircraft]].\n#* {{quote-journal|en|year=1998|work=Approach|volume=43|issue=10|page=10|pageurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=nT0w2bEwBDAC&pg=PA10|passage=I was horrified to see three '''grapes''' standing by the aircraft with the hose still connected.}}\n# {{senseid|en|head}} {{lb|en|AAVE|slang}} A person's [[head]].\n#: {{syn|en|Thesaurus:head}}\n\n=====Hyponyms=====\n{{sense|plants of genus ''Vitis''}}\n{{col|en\n| {{vern|Amur grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis amurensis|species}})|{{vern|arroyo grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}})\n| {{vern|bird grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis munsoniana|species}})|{{vern|bull grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis rotundifolia|species}})|{{vern|bullace grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis rotundifolia|species}})|{{vern|bunch grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis aestivalis|species}})|{{vern|bush grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis rupestris|species}}; {{taxlink|Vitis acerifolia|species}})\n| {{vern|canyon grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis arizonica|species}})|[[cat grape]] ({{taxlink|Vitis palmata|species}})|[[catbird grape]] ({{taxlink|Vitis palmata|species}})|{{vern|chicken grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}})|[[Concord grape]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis labrusca|species}} variety)|[[coon grape]] ({{taxlink|Ampelopsis cordata|species}}; {{taxfmt|Vitis labrusca|species}})\n| {{vern|downy grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis cinerea|species}})\n| {{vern|European grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vinifera|species}})|{{vern|everbearing grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis munsoniana|species}})\n| [[fox grape]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis labrusca|species}} et al.)|[[frost grape]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}})\n| grape neutral spirit\n| Mission grape|[[Missouri grape]] ({{taxlink|Vitis palmata|species}})|[[mountain grape]] ({{taxlink|Vitis rupestris|species}}, {{taxfmt|Berberis aquifolium|species}} (syn. {{taxfmt|Mahonia aquifolium|species}}))|{{vern|muscadine grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis rotundifolia|species}})|{{vern|mustang grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis candicans|species}})|{{vern|mustard grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis candicans|species}})\n| neutral grape spirit\n| {{vern|pigeon grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis aestivalis|species}})|{{vern|pinewoods grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis labrusca var. lincecumii|variety}})|[[plum grape]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis labrusca|species}} et al.)|{{vern|possum grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}}, {{taxlink|Vitis baileyana|species}}, {{taxfmt|Cissus|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|post-oak grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis labrusca var. lincecumii|variety}})\n| {{vern|racoon grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis labrusca|species}} et al., {{taxlink|Ampelopsis cordata|species}})|{{vern|river grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}})|{{vern|riverbank grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis riparia|species}})|{{vern|riverside grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}}; {{taxlink|Vitis riparia|species}})|[[rock grape]] ({{taxlink|Vitis rupestris|species}})|{{vern|rose grape}} ({{taxlink|Medinilla magnifica|species}})\n| {{vern|sandbeach grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis rupestris|species}})|[[sand grape]] ({{taxlink|Vitis rupestris|species}})| {{vern|shore grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis labrusca|species}} et al.)|{{vern|skunk grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis lambrusca|species}})|{{vern|slipskin grape}} ([[Concord grape]])|{{vern|sugar grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis rupestris|species}})|[[summer grape]] ({{taxlink|Vitis aestivalis|species}})\n| [[table grape]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|turkey grape}} ({{taxlink|Vitis labrusca var. lincecumii|variety}})\n| {{vern|wild grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}} spp., {{taxlink|Rhoicissus capensis|species}})|[[wine grape]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}} spp.)|[[winter grape]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}})| {{vern|wolf grape}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vulpina|species}}, {{taxfmt|Solanum dulcamara|species}})\n}}\n{{sense|plants of other genera}}\n{{col|en|\n| {{vern|bear's grape}} ({{taxfmt|Arctostaphylos uva-ursi|species}})|{{vern|Burmese grape}} ({{taxlink|Baccaurea ramiflora|species}})\n| {{vern|Cape grape|pl=s}} ({{taxlink|Cissus capensis|species}}, {{taxlink|Rhoicissus tomentosa|species}})\n| {{vern|dyer's grape}} ({{taxfmt|Phytolacca americana|species}})\n| [[grape cactus]] ({{taxlink|Mammillaria prolifera|species}})|[[grape fern]]s ({{taxfmt|Botrychium|genus}} spp.)|[[grapefruit]] {{taxfmt|Citrus paradisi|species}})|[[grape hyacinth]]s ({{taxfmt|Muscari|genus}} spp.)|[[grape ivy]] ({{taxfmt|Parthenocissus tricuspidata|species}})\n| {{vern|kangaroo grape}} ({{taxlink|Cissus antarctica|species}})\n| [[mangrove grape]] ({{taxfmt|Coccoloba uvifera|species}})\n| [[Oregon grape]] {{vern|Rocky Mountain grape}} ({{taxfmt|Berberis aquifolium|species}}, syn. {{taxfmt|Mahonia aquifolium|species}})\n| [[sea grape]]s<qq:various plants so called>|[[seaside grape]] ({{taxfmt|Coccoloba uvifera|species}})\n| [[tail grape]]s ({{taxlink|Artabotrys|genus}} spp.)\n}}\n\n=====Derived terms=====\n{{col|en\n|crangrape\n|dessert grape\n|grape cell\n|grapeful\n|grape jelly|grape juice\n|grape kernel\n|grapeless|grapelet|grapelike|grape-louse\n|graperita|grapery\n|grapeseed|grapeshot|grapeskin|grape smuggler,grape smugglers|grape-stone,grapestone|grapes of wrath|grape sugar\n|grape therapy|grapetini|grape tomato\n|[[grapevine]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}} spp.), [[grapevine]] {{lb|en|gossip}}\n|grape wine|grapewise\n|grapey\n|grapy\n|mare's teat grape|miller's grape\n|Niagara grape\n|peel me a grape\n|red grape\n|sour grapes|spoiled grape juice|squeeze-grape\n|table grape,tablegrape\n|white grape|winegrape,wine grape\n}}\n\n=====Related terms=====\n{{col|en|grappa\n|grapnel\n|grapple\n}}\n\n=====Translations=====\n{{trans-top|fruit}}\n* Abkhaz: {{t|ab|ажь}}\n* Afrikaans: {{t+|af|druif}}\n* Albanian: {{t+|sq|rrush|m}}\n* Altai:\n*: Southern Altai: {{t|alt|виноград}}, {{t|alt|ӱзӱм}} ''(raisin)''\n* Alviri-Vidari: {{t|avd|انگور|tr=angur}}\n* Amharic: {{t|am|ወይን}}\n* Arabic: {{t+|ar|عِنَب|m}}\n*: Egyptian Arabic: {{t|arz|عنب|m|tr=ʕanab|qq=collective}}, {{t|arz|عنبة|f|tr=ʕanaba|qq={{lg|singulative}}}}\n*: Hijazi Arabic: {{t|acw|عُنَب|m|tr=ʕunab|qq=collective}}\n*: Moroccan Arabic: {{t|ary|عنب|m|tr=ʕinab|qq=collective}}\n* Aragonese: {{t|an|uga|f}}, {{t|an|uba|f}}\n* Aramaic:\n*: Assyrian Neo-Aramaic: {{t|aii|ܥܲܢܒ݂ܵܐ|tr=ʿānwa|m}}\n*: Hebrew script: {{t|arc|עִנְבְּתָא|f|tr=ʿinbəṯā}}\n*: Syriac: {{t|arc|ܥܢܒܬܐ|f|tr=ʿinbəṯā}}\n* Archi: {{t|aqc|тӏуммул}}\n* Armenian: {{t+|hy|խաղող}}, {{t+|hy|ազոխ|q=unripe}}\n* Aromanian: {{t|rup|auã|f}}\n* Assamese: {{t|as|আঙুৰ}}, {{t|as|লতা-পনীয়ল}}, {{t|as|দাক্ষা}}\n* Asturian: {{t+|ast|uva|f}}\n* Aymara: {{t|ay|upasa}}\n* Azerbaijani: {{t+|az|üzüm}}\n* Bakhtiari: {{t|bqi|انگیر|tr=angir}}\n* Baluchi: {{t|bal|انگور|tr=angúr}}\n* Bashkir: {{t|ba|йөҙөм}}\n* Basque: {{t+|eu|mahats}}\n* Belarusian: {{t|be|вінагра́д|m}}\n* Bengali: {{t+|bn|আঙ্গুর}}, {{t+|bn|আঙুর}}, {{t+|bn|দ্রাক্ষা}}\n* Bikol:\n*: Central Bikol: {{t+|bcl|ubas}}\n* Breton: {{t+check|br|rezin}}, {{t-check|br|rezinenn|f|q=collective}}\n* Bulgarian: {{t|bg|гро́зде|n}}\n* Burmese: {{t+|my|စပျစ်သီး}}\n* Carpathian Rusyn: {{t|rue|гро́зно|n}}\n* Catalan: {{t+|ca|raïm|m}}\n* Chechen: {{t|ce|кемс}}\n* Chichewa: {{t|ny|mphesa}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Cantonese: {{t+|yue|提子|qq=colloquial}}, {{t|yue|葡提子}}, {{t|yue|葡萄|qq=formal}}\n*: Dungan: {{t|dng|путо}}\n*: Eastern Min: {{t|cdo|葡萄|tr=può-dò̤}}\n*: Hakka: {{t|hak|葡萄|tr=phù-thò}}\n*: Hokkien: {{t+|nan-hbl|葡萄|tr=phô-tô, pô-tô, phû-tô}}\n*: Mandarin: {{t+|cmn|葡萄}}, {{t+|cmn|提子|tr=tízi|qq=dialect}}\n*: Wu: {{t|wuu|葡萄}}\n* Chuvash: {{t|